# activity_wordpress

Repository for the WordPress dashboard exploration assignment.

Files:
- `page-exploring-dashboard.html` â€” HTML content you can paste into the WordPress page editor (Text/HTML mode) or into a Custom HTML block.

After cloning this repository into your AMPPS `www` directory, log into your local WordPress (usually http://localhost/your-site/wp-admin), create a new page, paste the HTML from `page-exploring-dashboard.html`, and publish.

Repository URL: <your-GitHub-repo-URL>
